<p>For this to work properly Zend_Soap_Wsdl should be refactored big time, its currently implemented quite slobbish and hardcoded in its XML building.</p>

<p>As a hack, though this is probably not desired, one could extend the addBindingOperation() function to take another parameter $soapHeaders with 'input', 'output' keys in the first level and key-&gt;params that map to attribute name and value in the second level.</p>

